==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reticent
<hw>Ret"i*cent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>reticens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>reticere</ets> to keep silence;
<ets>re-</ets> + <ets>tacere</ets> to be silent. See
<er>Tacit</er>.]</ety> <def>Inclined to keep silent; reserved;
uncommunicative.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reticle</ent>⟦br⟧
